title: Emmymade on Candy Creations, Eating Critters, and the Joys of Being a Curious Cook
description:
On her YouTube channel, Emmymade in Japan, Emmy Cho (aka Emmymade) explores food and recipes sent to her from fans all over the world. In this episode of Homemade, Emmymade dishes with Martie Duncan on recreating old recipes, growing up with classic cooking shows, feeding a young family, and eating bugs.
